` with `npm run docs:build`. Production and preview builds use distinct build-time `NEXT_PUBLIC_DOCS_BASE_PATH` values because Next.js inlines `basePath` during static export. The workflow deploys the production docs for `main` and publishes same-repository PR previews under `/pr-preview/pr-<number>/` when both the PR and its latest push changed docs-related files. Locally, the repo verifies the presence and wiring of docs files during E2E. The actual rendered Pages build is validated by GitHub Actions."},"555":{"id":"/project/verification-56","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"The CI workflow at `.github/workflows/ci.yml` runs package verification, Docker Compose validation, Helm chart lint/render checks, and the Docker-backed E2E suite. The container workflow at `.github/workflows/container.yml` builds and publishes the ingest image to GitHub Container Registry only after CI succeeds on `main`, producing `linux/amd64` and `linux/arm64` images under the same GHCR tags. The publish job then inspects the pushed manifest digest and fails if either platform is missing."},"556":{"id":"/project/verification-57","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Validate deployment artifacts locally with:"},"557":{"id":"/project/verification-58","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Run the local ingest benchmark with:"},"558":{"id":"/project/verification-59","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#deployment-artifact-checks","content":"Package publishability is checked with:"},"559":{"id":"/project/verification-60","page_id":"/project/verification","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/project/verification#when-to-add-e2e-coverage","content":"Add E2E assertions when documentation i